{"tid":2340541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有還押手足喺荔枝角收押所大叫聖誕快樂","createTime":"2020-12-25T14:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T15:52:25.000Z","uid":352288,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a03b1c096013892543a5841c3033afe462ab02c6","tid":2340541,"uid":352288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:21:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://fb.watch/2BHBzxL8Lh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2F2BHBzxL8Lh%2F&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=8bf1a5d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.watch/2BHBzxL8Lh/</a><br />\n<br />\n【有還押於荔枝角收押所的人士高呼聖誕快樂】<br />\n<br />\n今日為聖誕節正日，有還押於荔枝角收押所的人士高呼「聖誕快樂」、「精神啊」，本台記者拍攝期間亦有還押人士大聲高叫「何時會落山」<br />\n<br />\n攝：Thomas Ng<br />\n<br />\n【Protests】Remandees at Lai Chi Kok Reception Centre chants for Christmas <br />\n<br />\nRemandees at Lai Chi Kok Reception Centre chants for Christmas. Daily Record&rsquo;s reporters were met with a warm greeting by the remanded where they asked when we would leave, they also told us to keep the struggle on.<br />\n<br />\nVideo by Thomas Ng<br />\n<br />\n如欲支持Daily Record記者<br />\n歡迎大家以銀行入數資助形式支持我們<br />\n匯豐銀行 HSBC : 484855036838<br />\nIG : <a href=\"http://daily.record.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdaily.record.hk&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=96f6e075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">daily.record.hk</a><br />\nTwitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ailyRecord (Hong Kong)<br />\nMewe: Daily Record (Hong Kong)"},{"pid":"f379d68fa08d854cb7f643b8a80bd18cddf45960","tid":2340541,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:21:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af6fa9697eb96eeb9f9f77a1f860a47eb8802b19","tid":2340541,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:21:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a69e5c028f67c97cda0bb9dfc7ed5d8a66a07274","tid